arts.ttl: When is Colombia vs Ecuador? Times, how to watch on TV and stream online
arts.sum: On matchday 12 of South America’s World Cup qualifying competition, Colombia continue their bid for a return to the global tournament as they host an Ecuador team chasing back-to-back berths at the event. The CONMEBOL 2026 World Cup qualifier between Colombia and Ecuador will be played at the Estadio Metropolitano Roberto Meléndez in Baranquilla, Colombia, on Tuesday November 19, 2024.

arts.ttl: Chelsea face midfield dilemma as they sweat over Romeo Lavia fitness - with Moises Caicedo and Enzo Fernandez returning from international duty just 48 hours before Leicester clash
arts.sum: Chelsea are facing a midfield conundrum for their early Saturday visit to Leicester after Romeo Lavia missed both of Belgium's matches due to a hamstring complaint.
